      div.description
        p Hi! I'm Sergio, I'm 21 years old and I'm from Buenos Aires, Argentina. I'm a Front End Developer with some years of experience. I'm working in a company named <a href="//www.promaker.com.ar" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Promaker</a> doing CSS layouts and JS in a little team. We do some web sites or intranets for other companies and digital marketing.
        p I studied electromechanic in high school <a href="//goo.gl/maps/DxODg" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">E.T. N°11 D.E. 6 "Manuel Belgrano"</a> and when I graduate (2011) I did <a href="//mejorando.la" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Mejorando.la's</a> courses of <a href="//mejorando.la/online" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Diseño Web</a> and <a href="//mejorando.la/frontend" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">FrontEnd Profesional</a>.
        p I like share code in my <a href="//github.com/sergiodxa" target="_blank">Github account</a> and write articles and tutorials who I publish in <a href="//medium.com/@sergiodxa">Medium</a>. I did some libraries in JavaScript and LESS who I use in my work and release them with MIT license in Github.
        p I like to use tools who help me in my work, like LESS to pre-process the CSS and Gulp to automate all my repetitive tasks.
